{"tid":93924,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"不怕「臭名」！Samsung 正式確認 Galaxy Note 8","createTime":"2017-01-24T21:10:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-25T05:35:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f1ed375cef11069fcdba56b68604905ccf42347","tid":93924,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T21:10:17.000Z","msg":"Note 7 事件發生後，大家都認為 Galaxy Note 這個系列已經「玩完」。就算之後再出新的大屏手機也不能再叫 &ldquo;Note&rdquo;，否則只會令人聯想起 Note 7 事件。不過看來 Samsung 並不這樣想！ <br />\n<br />\nSamsung 流動業務總監昨天在 Note 7 事件調查發佈會後接受訪問，表明 Galaxy Note 系列會繼續下去。更加明言下一部就是 Galaxy Note 8：「我將會帶來一部更好、更安全、更創新的 Note 8。」 <br />\n為何 Samsung 不怕 Galaxy Note 品牌已經變質？他解釋最大原因是現在還有很多 Note 系列的忠實用家。 <br />\n<br />\n昨天 Samsung 公開 Note 7 調查結果後，媒體和用戶的反應還算不錯。Samsung 亦確實有承擔事件的責任，並清楚列出今後的「8 步計劃」來防止同類事件發生。究竟是否足以令 Note 8 擺脫陰霾就要拭目以待了。 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn0.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Ov3aFpReAcFNe4juhlvmigk23h0 /800x0/filters:no_upscale  /cdn0.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_asset/file/7852621/_Infographic__8_point_battery_safety_check__1_.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn0.vox-cdn.com%2Fthumbor%2FOv3aFpReAcFNe4juhlvmigk23h0%20%2F800x0%2Ffilters%3Ano_upscale%20%20%2Fcdn0.vox-cdn.com%2Fuploads%2Fchorus_asset%2Ffile%2F7852621%2F_Infographic__8_point_battery_safety_check__1_.jpg&h=f84b5a49&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.price.com.hk/news/2017/01/24/12/%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E8%87%AD%E5%90%8Dsamsung-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D-galaxy-note-8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.price.com.hk%2Fnews%2F2017%2F01%2F24%2F12%2F%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2580%2595%25E8%2587%25AD%25E5%2590%258Dsamsung-%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25AA%258D-galaxy-note-8&d=jlMUGUNBB2JG8BQortsepQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=8a84008a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.price.com.hk/news/2017/01/24/12/%E4%B8%8D%E6%80%95%E8%87%AD%E5%90%8Dsamsung-%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%A2%BA%E8%AA%8D-galaxy-note-8</a>"},